EN: The fisherman caught fish with a stick.

ZH: 棍子在古代被用来制造武器。
EN: Sticks were used to make weapons in ancient times.

ZH: 小偷用棍子打开锁。
EN: The thief used a stick to open the lock.

ZH: 她做了一个棍子预防蛇的袭击。
EN: She made a stick to protect against snake attacks.

ZH: 舞蹈表演中使用了棍子作为道具。
EN: Sticks were used as props in the dance performance.

ZH: 他练习了很久才学会了吉他弹奏的技巧。
EN: He practiced for a long time to learn the guitar playing skills.

ZH: 我家里有一条很大的狗。
EN: There is a big dog in my house.

ZH: 他手里拿着一根打狗的棍子。
EN: He held a stick used to hit dogs in his hand.

ZH: 她正在练习如何在野外生存。
EN: She is practicing how to survive in the wilderness.

ZH: 我看见她在树林里探险。
EN: I saw her exploring in the forest.

ZH: 他在海边捡拾漂流木。
EN: He picked up driftwood at the seaside.

ZH: 她用一根棍子指向远处。
EN: She pointed to the distance with a stick.

ZH: 他在山上捡了一根长长的棍子。
EN: He picked up a long stick on the mountain.

ZH: 喜欢户外活动的人通常会带一根棍子。
EN: People who enjoy outdoor activities usually carry a stick.

ZH: 躲避野兽时，要用棍子自卫。
EN: When avoiding wild animals, use a stick for self-defense.

ZH: 刚下雨的路面很湿滑，要用棍子稳住身体。
EN: The road is slippery after rain, use a stick to stabilize your body.
